original_title: 石田亜佑美 バースデーイベントDX ～９期メンの２人を迎えて～
overview: Fanclub exclusive birthday event: Ishida Ayumi's 16th birthday. The theme of the event is based on Morning Musume. Concert Tour 2011 Haru Shin Souseiki Fantasy DX ~9ki Mem wo Mukaete~, featuring 9th Generation members Ikuta Erina and Suzuki Kanon. Held at Tokyo FM Hall.
title: Ishida Ayumi Birthday Event DX ~9ki Mem no Futari wo Mukaete~
